<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 22:07:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列的“高强度”行动即将结束。但内塔尼亚胡不希望加沙战争结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-intense-operations-are-almost-over-but-netanyahu-doesnt-want-the-war-to-end/0000018f-c57d-da41-a9cf-d57f55370000</link><description>以色列政治或军事机构中没有人认为加沙战争即将结束。但内塔尼亚胡不会谈论停火，甚至不会将人质带回家，也不会谈论停火后的第二天，他当然不会听到任何有关提前选举的谈论</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-intense-operations-are-almost-over-but-netanyahu-doesnt-want-the-war-to-end/0000018f-c57d-da41-a9cf-d57f55370000</guid></item><item><title>工作日有道路施工吗？以色列交通运输部副部长解释公众将如何获得补偿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/roadworks-on-weekdays-deputy-transport-minister-explains-how-public-will-be-compensated/0000018f-c4b1-d323-a98f-dff96ab50000</link><description>特拉维夫至耶路撒冷 1 号高速公路将在下周而不是周末关闭，极端正统派交通运输部副部长乌里·马克列夫 (Uri Maklev) 表示，“我们将通过加强对安息日的遵守来补偿以色列人”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 19:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/roadworks-on-weekdays-deputy-transport-minister-explains-how-public-will-be-compensated/0000018f-c4b1-d323-a98f-dff96ab50000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查：以色列战时联盟出现裂痕，甘茨对内塔尼亚胡的领先优势缩小</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/poll-gantzs-lead-over-netanyahu-narrows-as-wartime-coalition-shows-cracks/0000018f-c5b8-d323-a98f-dff9cfdc0000</link><description>受访者被问及他们认为谁更适合担任总理，在所有比较中，内塔尼亚胡领先</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 19:43:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/poll-gantzs-lead-over-netanyahu-narrows-as-wartime-coalition-shows-cracks/0000018f-c5b8-d323-a98f-dff9cfdc0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日左右，与杰里·宋飞 (Jerry Seinfeld) 一起哭泣。但请为加沙人留一滴眼泪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-29/ty-article/.highlight/cry-with-jerry-seinfeld-about-october-7-but-save-a-tear-for-the-gazans/0000018f-c579-db12-a3ff-c77fc0b40000</link><description>巴里·韦斯和宋飞正需要多少同理心才能停下来，认为也许“暴徒”（他们在《自由新闻》采访中提到亲巴勒斯坦运动时也正遭受痛苦）是如此微不足道，我仍然惊讶的是他们俩都无法鼓起勇气</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 18:27:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-29/ty-article/.highlight/cry-with-jerry-seinfeld-about-october-7-but-save-a-tear-for-the-gazans/0000018f-c579-db12-a3ff-c77fc0b40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称已控制加沙-埃及边境战略走廊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/israeli-army-says-it-took-control-of-strategic-corridor-along-gaza-egypt-border/0000018f-c56a-d8a8-afff-effe50780000</link><description>这条非军事化的狭窄走廊横跨埃及边境加沙一侧，全长 14 公里；以色列国防军还承认，尚未完全控制加沙地带北部</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 17:59:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/israeli-army-says-it-took-control-of-strategic-corridor-along-gaza-egypt-border/0000018f-c56a-d8a8-afff-effe50780000</guid></item><item><title>“需要紧急选举”：加沙战争内阁部长猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡；总理：他们希望结束战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/urgent-elections-needed-war-cabinet-ministers-slam-netanyahu-pm-they-want-to-end-war/0000018f-c4ee-db12-a3ff-c7fe72510000</link><description>中间派战时内阁成员加迪·艾森科特表示，总理对加沙的成就“宣扬虚假的妄想”，并且“惨败”地实现了目标</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 16:57:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/urgent-elections-needed-war-cabinet-ministers-slam-netanyahu-pm-they-want-to-end-war/0000018f-c4ee-db12-a3ff-c7fe72510000</guid></item><item><title>“犹太复国主义者到达之前，帕洛阿尔托要好得多”：斯坦福大学加沙营地的一天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palo-alto-was-much-nicer-before-the-zionists-came-a-day-at-stanfords-gaza-encampment/0000018f-c4c9-d4da-a58f-f7d9191c0000</link><description>在该大学的抗议现场，一位最近称哈马斯和真主党为“荣誉人物”的奥克兰伊玛目对一名亲以色列的犹太学生说：“你们都变得像纳粹了”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 16:32:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palo-alto-was-much-nicer-before-the-zionists-came-a-day-at-stanfords-gaza-encampment/0000018f-c4c9-d4da-a58f-f7d9191c0000</guid></item><item><title>巴西总统召回驻以色列大使 加沙战争外交危机加剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/brazils-president-recalls-ambassador-to-israel-intensifying-diplomatic-crisis-over-gaza/0000018f-c4e6-d4da-a58f-f7ff7f6b0000</link><description>巴西官员表示，此次召回是由于以色列对大使的“羞辱”，当时以色列外交部长召集他强制参观大屠杀纪念馆，以谴责卢拉总统将加沙攻势与大屠杀相比较的言论</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 16:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/brazils-president-recalls-ambassador-to-israel-intensifying-diplomatic-crisis-over-gaza/0000018f-c4e6-d4da-a58f-f7ff7f6b0000</guid></item><item><title>请欢迎您的新室友“老大哥”：一名被关押在加沙的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/welcome-your-new-big-brother-housemates-israelis-held-in-gaza/0000018f-c3bf-de7a-a5df-c3ff592f0000</link><description>以色列版的电视节目《老大哥》新一季回归，仿佛公众现在需要的是一部关于以色列人在封闭空间中受到监视的节目。新的在线活动将确保你无法逃避现实</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 15:45:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/welcome-your-new-big-brother-housemates-israelis-held-in-gaza/0000018f-c3bf-de7a-a5df-c3ff592f0000</guid></item><item><title>在内塔尼亚胡和以色列回答这三个问题之前，加沙战争不会结束</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-war-wont-end-until-netanyahu-and-israel-answer-these-three-questions/0000018f-c3db-dbf7-adef-e3fb1ba70000</link><description>问题很尖锐。首先，加沙战争会结束吗？如何结束？之后会发生什么？以色列和巴勒斯坦人未来必须何去何从才能确保这种地狱不再重演？每个问题都有一个选择和一个答案</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 15:15:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-war-wont-end-until-netanyahu-and-israel-answer-these-three-questions/0000018f-c3db-dbf7-adef-e3fb1ba70000</guid></item><item><title>七名以色列警察因在巴勒斯坦人脸上盖上大卫之星而受到审判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/seven-israeli-cops-expected-to-be-tried-for-stamping-star-of-david-on-palestinians-face/0000018f-c41d-d0b7-abdf-ccbfd4d30000</link><description>参与逮捕东耶路撒冷难民营22岁居民的警察涉嫌虐待、严重袭击、妨碍司法公正和其他罪行</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:48:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/seven-israeli-cops-expected-to-be-tried-for-stamping-star-of-david-on-palestinians-face/0000018f-c41d-d0b7-abdf-ccbfd4d30000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列士兵在拉法爆炸中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-rafah/0000018f-c457-d4da-a58f-f7df5f310000</link><description>这些士兵是参谋军士。阿米尔·加利洛夫，20 岁，参谋军士。乌里·巴尔·奥尔（Uri Bar Or）和参谋中士。伊多·阿佩尔，21 岁</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:47:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/three-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-blast-in-rafah/0000018f-c457-d4da-a58f-f7df5f310000</guid></item><item><title>西班牙承认巴勒斯坦，内塔尼亚胡在以色列欢迎西班牙反伊斯兰党领导人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-welcomes-spanish-anti-islam-party-leader-in-israel-as-spain-recognized-palestine/0000018f-c484-da41-a9cf-d5bef18a0000</link><description>西班牙极右翼 Vox 党领袖圣地亚哥·阿巴斯卡 (Santiago Abascal) 因伊斯兰恐惧症、反移民言论和反 LGBTQ 立场而受到批评，他来到以色列会见内塔尼亚胡，谴责西班牙左翼政府</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-welcomes-spanish-anti-islam-party-leader-in-israel-as-spain-recognized-palestine/0000018f-c484-da41-a9cf-d5bef18a0000</guid></item><item><title>汉娜·阿伦特将如何回应以色列被指控犯有反人类罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-hannah-arendt-would-respond-to-israel-being-accused-of-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-c3e2-d822-a58f-d7fe35a90000</link><description>阿伦特逃离了纳粹，并因报道艾希曼审判而闻名，他坚信国际刑事法院可以防止种族灭绝。那么她会支持国际刑事法院对以色列和哈马斯领导人发出的潜在逮捕令吗？</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 12:58:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-29/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-hannah-arendt-would-respond-to-israel-being-accused-of-crimes-against-humanity/0000018f-c3e2-d822-a58f-d7fe35a90000</guid></item><item><title>妮基·黑利在以色列军队炮弹上涂写暴力信息，引发愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/nikki-haley-scrawls-violent-message-on-idf-artillery-shell-sparks-criticism/0000018f-c413-de7a-a5df-c77f50da0000</link><description>在参观10月7日以色列南部遭到袭击的地点时，失败的共和党总统候选人加入了签署以色列国防军导弹的潮流。 “你能带她回去吗？”一位和平活动家反驳道，“我们已经有了一个本-格维尔”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 12:27:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/nikki-haley-scrawls-violent-message-on-idf-artillery-shell-sparks-criticism/0000018f-c413-de7a-a5df-c77f50da0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人向以色列城镇开枪 以色列国防军称无人伤亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-shoot-at-israeli-town-idf-says-no-casualties/0000018f-c3cd-d822-a58f-d7dd35bb0000</link><description>埃梅克·赫弗地区委员会主席表示，这起事件并不罕见，该地区的枪击事件“已经成为每天”发生的事情，居民证明他们生活在恐惧之中</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 11:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-shoot-at-israeli-town-idf-says-no-casualties/0000018f-c3cd-d822-a58f-d7dd35bb0000</guid></item><item><title>Robo-Zelda：以色列军队的无人装甲运兵车在拉法被发现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/robo-zelda-israeli-armys-remote-controlled-apc-robots-spotted-in-gazas-rafah/0000018f-c38d-dade-adef-efaf644d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦当地人在社交媒体上发布了在拉法运行的机器人的视频片段，他们称它们为“诱杀坦克”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 11:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/robo-zelda-israeli-armys-remote-controlled-apc-robots-spotted-in-gazas-rafah/0000018f-c38d-dade-adef-efaf644d0000</guid></item><item><title>遍体鳞伤：以色列反战抗议者受伤被送上法庭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/bruised-and-battered-israeli-anti-war-protesters-brought-to-court-with-injuries/0000018f-c32d-d822-a58f-d73db8840000</link><description>在法庭延长拘留听证会上，其中一名妇女的手臂上有石膏，另一名妇女的脖子上有瘀伤的迹象。她的律师说，其中一名抗议者“在逮捕过程中被按在地上并被窒息”</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 11:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/bruised-and-battered-israeli-anti-war-protesters-brought-to-court-with-injuries/0000018f-c32d-d822-a58f-d73db8840000</guid></item><item><title>亲以色列团体帮助共和党议员击败拿大屠杀开玩笑的极右翼共和党人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-groups-help-defeat-far-right-republican-who-joked-about-holocaust/0000018f-c25a-d822-a58f-d75e37e10000</link><description>AIPAC 附属超级政治行动委员会和共和党犹太联盟的参与是 2024 年选举周期中最重要的参与之一</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 06:46:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/pro-israel-groups-help-defeat-far-right-republican-who-joked-about-holocaust/0000018f-c25a-d822-a58f-d75e37e10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的致命疏忽威胁到美国对拉法行动的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/after-israels-callous-carelessness-in-rafah-washington-now-calls-the-shots/0000018f-c0d4-df6b-a3ff-eafea9a80000</link><description>本周加沙发生的两起大规模人员伤亡事件表明，国际社会不再愿意听取以色列的解释，对以色列国防军也不再像七个月前那样耐心。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 03:01:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-29/ty-article/.premium/after-israels-callous-carelessness-in-rafah-washington-now-calls-the-shots/0000018f-c0d4-df6b-a3ff-eafea9a80000</guid></item></channel></rss>